songs.title: ​how many secrets can you keep?*
songs.lyrics:
I haven't slept alone
In a
Minute
Like to push my own
Limits
Is it
Something that I've grown
Into
Been too
Young for too long

You think I'm lyin' to ya
Yup
I been lying to ya
Yup
Getting kinda hard to breathe
With these hands all over me
Something you don't wanna see
So I think im gonna keep on
Lyin' to ya
